tspan.tspan: Advancing motive power from the start
For over 100 years, EnerSys® has developed and deployed
energy storage technologies for applications ranging from
material handling equipment, to critical data networks, to
deep space satellites and more. For material handling,
EnerSys® puts “Total Power in Motion” for your fleet –
maximizing operational throughput while minimizing
ownership costs.
Advanced data analytics & application modeling
True optimization across broad technology portfolio
Advanced fleet energy reporting and management
Extensive field service & support network
Sustainability: Not just a commitment, but a priority.
Sustainability at EnerSys® is about more than just the benefits
and impacts of our products. It is a fundamental part of how
we manage our operations.
Global sustainability initiatives for renewables,
grid optimization and EV charging
Our Battery Recycling Program has a 99% recycle rate
on lead acid batteries
Targets for continued improvement across environmental,
social and governance areas
